Package com.ibm.team.repository.common.validation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IItemValidator
    Common validator that can be used by clients to validate item properties to ensure the values conform to repository constraints.
    IPropertyConstraintErrorStatus
    Base type for any validation error generated by IItemValidator.
    IStringSizeConstraintErrorStatus
    Specialized status for string size constraint violations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PropertyConstraintException
    Exception which indicates that an item violates the constraints set out in its model.
